title: Extended New York Undercover Pt. 2 ft Jess Hilarious | Ep. 76
itunes:title: Extended New York Undercover Pt. 2 ft Jess Hilarious | Ep. 76
description:
The crew remembers Charlie Murphy and tells stories from times with him and his impact on comedy. Jess Hilarious stops thru to talk about her experience on Wild N Out and doing comedy with Martin Lawrence and Mike Epps. Karlous brings perspective on Janet Jackson and her divorce, Aries Spears on The 5150 show plus a legendary old school battle. Plus D.C. talks about The Chris Brown comedy tour.
